	   <tr><td colspan=2>Talisman drops of Zlandicar...as far as i know he drops it every time. (at least he has every time we have killed him, and we kill him often)Not a hard fight if you have the right ppl, done it with anywhere from 23-50 ppl just depending whose onlne. As far as who gets it...yeah its all/all but IMHO designed more for melee hybrid classes, but that doesnt stop me from puttin my name in the hat for the awarding of it. Got one tonight and its a nice haste upgrade to my dropped poa belt, and is replacing my ancient seahorse hide cloak.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
